ck-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"border-bottom-style:none;border-bottom-width:0px;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-bottom:0;margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><strong>Location<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck\u00e7ak\u0131l Mevkii<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><summary>Properties<\/summary>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">Waterfront with private beach and pool, with a beautiful view of the harbour and the Castellorizo (Meis) island against the sunset.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Very close to old city centre and to the harbour (400 m).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Rooms with balcony (sea view) with 2 or 3 beds, TV, A\/C, shower &amp; WC, phone and hair dryer, 24-hr room service, generator.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Open buffet breakfasts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Terrace, 3 bar\/snacks, restaurant and parking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">Outdoor activities offered by Dragoman: SCUBA diving, sea kayak, hiking, biking, coasteering.<\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><summary>Notes<\/summary>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">Free for children 0-6 years of age accompanying two adults<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">7-12 years stay at a room with Dbl + Chld<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">&nbsp;Half-board supplement 10\u20ac\/day<\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\"><summary>Prices<\/summary>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.dragoman-turkey.com\/en\/reservation-and-contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Please contact us<\/a>&nbsp;for up to date prices and availability.<\/p>\n<\/details>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-a7dce961 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-color:#e1e2e4;border-width:1px;border-radius:8px;background-color:#fafafa\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-service-name has-medium-font-size\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);font-style:normal;font-weight:700\">1 * Hotel<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"670\" height=\"363\" src=\"https:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/pansiyon.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-413\" srcset=\"http:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/pansiyon.jpg 670w, http:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/pansiyon-300x163.jpg 300w, http:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/pansiyon-416x225.jpg 416w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flex wp-container